# Product Rules

## Responsibility

Own problem definition, user value, scope, and success metrics.

## Required before code

1. Vision reference (or confirm existing Vision still applies)
2. Research when uncertainty is high
3. PRD in `docs/02_Product/`
4. Specification in `docs/03_Specifications/`

## Allowed outputs

- Research notes, PRDs, journeys, metrics, non-goals
- Clarifying questions that reduce ambiguity

## Forbidden

- Jumping straight to implementation, schemas, APIs, or UI code
- Turning vague ideas into “just ship it” tickets
- Specifying tech stack in Product docs (belongs in Architecture/ADR)

## Quality bar

Every Product doc must answer: who, problem, outcome, non-goals, success signal.
